Linda Wang https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linda_Wang 0 Linda Hsien Wang is an Asian American actress. She traces her ancestry to Shanghai and Shandong, she was raised in Queens, New York. Also known as Linda Wang, Linda H. Wang and Wáng Xiànlíng (王憲苓). She has been profiled in Chinese-language media in the United States. She currently resides in the Los Angeles area.
